  <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">　　采用AMD Radeon HD 8750M 独立显卡，带给你鲜活、生动的视觉效果，享受到更出色的视觉表现力。配备的2GB超大容量显存更为高清视频和游戏提供了有力保证。<br />\r\n    *选配</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"cut1\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 920px; position: relative;\">\r\n    <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/htmlfeature/images/NPC/300e5v/2.jpg\" class=\"gomeImgLoad\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n    <div class=\"block2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; position: absolute; left: 80px; top: 85px; width: 345px;\">\r\n    <h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 26px; font-weight: normal; word-wrap: break-word;\">大容量的存储</h2>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">　　采用标准规格笔记本硬盘，可扩充至500GB的存储空间。使得笔记本在移动过程中，也能够享受到海量的影、音存储。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"cut1\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 920px; position: relative;\">\r\n    <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/htmlfeature/images/NPC/300e5v/3.jpg\" class=\"gomeImgLoad\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n    <div class=\"block3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 60px; width: 390px;\">\r\n    <h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 26px; font-weight: normal; word-wrap: break-word;\">内置光驱，功能全面</h2>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">　　内置光驱，功能全面 笔记本内置标准DVD双层刻录光驱，可以方便你随时安装应用程序、游戏，以及播放DVD电影。并且还可以通过刻录功能，随时备份你的重要数据。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"cut1\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 920px; position: relative;\">\r\n    <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/htmlfeature/images/NPC/300e5v/4.jpg\" class=\"gomeImgLoad\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n    <div class=\"block4\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 80px; width: 390px;\">\r\n    <h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 26px; font-weight: normal; word-wrap: break-word;\">防眩光屏幕</h2>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">　　采用防眩光LED背光屏幕，不会受到外界强烈光线的影响，可以清晰的欣赏视频、图片，即使在户外阳光照射下，也可以清晰显示出屏幕的内容，有效保护眼睛。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"cut1\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 920px; position: relative;\">\r\n    <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/htmlfeature/images/NPC/300e5v/5.jpg\" class=\"gomeImgLoad\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n    <div class=\"block5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 80px; width: 390px;\">\r\n    <h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 26px; font-weight: normal; word-wrap: break-word;\">智能触控板技术</h2>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">　　符合人体工程学的全尺寸键盘设计，加上优化的键距调整，可以让你体验到舒适的打字感受。专为Windows 8优化的智能触控板，可以让你通过触控板的简单操作，就能实现Windows 8的各项操作。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"cut1\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 920px; position: relative;\">\r\n    <h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; fo